  <div id="modal" >
    <div class="modal-message">
      <h2>
      <ol>
          <li>The objective of the game is to crack the code i.e. guess the sequence of colours.</li>
          <li>To make your guess, select the colour you want to place on the board and click on the hole.</li>
          <li>You can submit your guess once all the 4 holes are filled. Colours can be repeated.</li>
          <li>After you submit your guess, grade pegs will appear. Red indicates a correct colour is present in the correct position and white indicates a correct colour is present in the wrong position. No grade is given for colours that are not in the code</li>
          <li>The order of grade pegs assigned DO NOT indicate which guess peg is given red or white.</li>
          <li>You have to guess the correct code by the end of 10 tries.</li>
      </ol>
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>
